CNCP v1 22607
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6404: Show location of `>>>` / `/deep/` in the `...combinators have been deprecated` message",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:49.125622+00:00",
  "text": "Show location of `>>>` / `/deep/` in the `...combinators have been deprecated` message\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\n\r\nWhen using `>>>` or `/deep/` (or probably also `v-deep`) combinators the warning message doesn't provide the location of where these combinators were used:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15625235/182706002-26c4b1c5-ded7-48e1-82af-2bd51b5febc3.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\n\r\nShow the filename / line of the `>>>`/`/deep/`/`v-deep` combinator",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request",
    "scope: compiler",
    ":cake: p2-nice-to-have"
  ],
